      <file>docs/assessments/bff-ai-extraction-assessment-2026-05-20.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Refined ADR-013 (2026-05-20) requires this facade for external CRUD→AI consumers. The
      assessment identified Finance / Workspace / Jobs / Dataverse / Filters / Endpoints as
      external consumers (CLAUDE.md PF-3 records ~59 files reality vs spec's 20). Phase 1 task
      014 + 011 + 015 produce the precise inventory. Interface granularity per consumer concern:
      `IBriefingAi` (Workspace briefing), `IInvoiceAi` (Finance invoice extraction),
      `IRecordMatchingAi`, `IWorkspacePrefillAi`. Other interfaces may emerge from Phase 1.
    </background>
    <dependencies><dependency task="037" status="not-started">Phase 3 BASELINE complete</dependency><dependency task="007" status="not-started">UQ-07 facade granularity confirmed</dependency></dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read ADR-007 SpeFileStore + actual SpeFileStore.cs source to understand canonical facade shape</step>
    <step order="2">Identify required methods per consumer category from Phase 1 inventory (task 011 usage map) — what does each consumer actually call?</step>
    <step order="3">Define 4+ small interfaces (one per concern) — methods MUST match observed usage</step>
    <step order="4">Create implementation classes wrapping existing IOpenAiClient / IPlaybookService</step>
    <step order="5">Add DI registration in `Services/Ai/AnalysisServicesModule.cs` or `AiModule.cs` (DON'T remove existing)</step>
    <step order="6">Update CLAUDE.md Decisions Made with the chosen interface list</step>
    <step order="7">build + test (±5% baseline)</step>
    <step order="8">Commit (single, scoped to facade introduction; no consumer migration)</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md status</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="dotnet">build, test</tool>
    <tool name="git">single commit</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PublicContracts/IBriefingAi.cs</output>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PublicContracts/IInvoiceAi.cs</output>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PublicContracts/IRecordMatchingAi.cs</output>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PublicContracts/IWorkspacePrefillAi.cs</output>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PublicContracts/*Ai.cs (implementations)</output>
